snippet.title: Sainthood | Cozy Strategy Game | Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1748600/Sainthood/

Sainthood is a cozy strategy game about serving your community. Explore a miniature world and help the townsfolk by constructing buildings, delivering resources, and volunteering. Pray and attend to other spiritual activities as you rise to become a Saint!
